#: upstream/_versions/main/guides/security-openid-connect-client-reference.adoc:202
#, no-wrap
msgid "Inject tokens"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: upstream/_versions/main/guides/security-openid-connect-client-reference.adoc:205
msgid "You can inject `Tokens` that use `OidcClient` internally. `Tokens` can be used to acquire the access tokens and refresh them if necessary:"
