#. type: delimited block -
#: upstream/_versions/main/guides/security-openid-connect-client-reference.adoc:255
#: upstream/_versions/main/guides/security-openid-connect-client-reference.adoc:283
#: upstream/_versions/main/guides/security-openid-connect-client-reference.adoc:316
#: upstream/_versions/main/guides/security-openid-connect-client-reference.adoc:348
